title: Normal wins question
body:
I was just looking at my profile page and saw I had around 736 or so normal wins but when I got into the after game screen I see that it is actually 664 not even 700, I assume that normal wins on your profile page includes twisted treeline wins as well? or is there something weird going on here? 
Thanks :)

replies.body: I think it includes Twisted Treeline and the other game modes. I'm not sure about the latter, though.
